body.p:
The view has a simple layout, with most of its space occupied by a message area. On its right side, there is a toolbar holding the following buttons:
Clear - Erases all the displayed messages;
Lock scroll - Disables the automatic scrolling when new messages are appended in the view. The maximum number of lines displayed in the console (length of the buffer) can be modified in the Preferences page. By default this value is set to 100.
